DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
9737::$$$message_0098_0000_0000$$$::"So about the other Servants..."[lr]::
9738::$$$message_0098_0000_0001$$$::"Please wait, Shirou. Someone has entered the gate of this property."::
9739::$$$message_0098_0001_0000$$$::"What? You can sense something like that...?[lr]::
9740::$$$message_0098_0001_0001$$$::Oh crap, it's already so late! This is bad. Sakura must be back!"::
9741::$$$message_0098_0002_0000$$$::The doorbell rings, and from the front entrance...[lr]::
9742::$$$message_0098_0002_0001$$$::I hear Sakura's voice.[lr]::
9743::$$$message_0098_0002_0002$$$::"I'm coming in."::
9744::$$$message_0098_0003_0000$$$::"Saber, sorry but..."[lr]::
9745::$$$message_0098_0003_0001$$$::"Yes, I know. I will retire to my room, so please do not mind me."[lr]::
9746::$$$message_0098_0003_0002$$$::Saber goes back to her room.::
9747::$$$message_0098_0004_0000$$$::Almost as if switching with Saber...[lr]::
9748::$$$message_0098_0004_0001$$$::"I'm home. Good, good. You came home early like I asked you to."[lr]::
9749::$$$message_0098_0004_0002$$$::Tohsaka walks in, laden with shopping bags.[lr]::
9750::$$$message_0098_0004_0003$$$::"Thank you for having me again, Senpai. It's rare for you to be home so early."[lr]::
9751::$$$message_0098_0004_0004$$$::Sakura walks in, smiling happily.::
9752::$$$message_0098_0005_0000$$$::"Okay. Everything is ready. I'm going to get started."[lr]::
9753::$$$message_0098_0005_0001$$$::Tohsaka psychs herself up and heads to the kitchen.[lr]::
9754::$$$message_0098_0005_0002$$$::"Senpai...? Um, about dinner tonight..."::
9755::$$$message_0098_0006_0000$$$::"You don't have to worry about it since it's Tohsaka's turn today. You prepared breakfast for us, so leave dinner to us. She and I will handle dinner while Tohsaka's staying here."[lr]::
9756::$$$message_0098_0006_0001$$$::"Oh...v-very well. If you say so, then I will have to oblige."[lr]::
9757::$$$message_0098_0006_0002$$$::Sakura quietly sits down.[lr]::
9758::$$$message_0098_0006_0003$$$::I hear a fiery, boisterous sound coming from the kitchen, but I see nothing of Tohsaka.::
9759::$$$message_0098_0007_0000$$$::"I guess I can trust her..."[lr]::
9760::$$$message_0098_0007_0001$$$::I should stay in my room until dinner's ready, considering Saber's waiting there.::
9761::$$$message_0098_0008_0000$$$::"I'm going to rest in my room. If Fuji-nee comes, tell her she should prepare the bath herself for a change."[lr]::
9762::$$$message_0098_0008_0001$$$::"Oh...okay. Please go relax, Senpai. I will come and get you once dinner is ready."::
9763::$$$message_0098_0009_0000$$$::"Yeah. Oh by the way, don't forget to knock when you come into my room."[lr]::
9764::$$$message_0098_0009_0001$$$::It's a little before six o'clock. I figure dinner will be ready around seven o'clock.::
9765::$$$message_0098_0010_0000$$$::I return to my room and find Saber sleeping in the room next door.::
9766::$$$message_0098_0011_0000$$$::"Bummer. I thought I could talk to her a little more."[lr]::
9767::$$$message_0098_0011_0001$$$::I click my tongue with disappointment and sit down.[lr]::
9768::$$$message_0098_0011_0002$$$::"Wait a minute. What am I thinking? There's nothing else I can talk to her about apart from the Holy Grail War."[lr]::
9769::$$$message_0098_0011_0003$$$::Besides, I don't know how to act around Saber.::
9770::$$$message_0098_0012_0000$$$::"Oh well. If she's asleep, I'll just let her rest."[lr]::
9771::$$$message_0098_0012_0001$$$::I mutter to myself and stare at the hands of the clock.[lr]::
9772::$$$message_0098_0012_0002$$$::Last night Saber, Tohsaka, and I ate dinner.[lr]::
9773::$$$message_0098_0012_0003$$$::But today, Sakura and Fuji-nee are in the mix as well, making it five people.::
9774::$$$message_0098_0013_0000$$$::"Oh...actually...Saber can't join."[lr]::
9775::$$$message_0098_0013_0001$$$::As long as Fuji-nee and Sakura are around, I can't have Saber come out of her room.[lr]::
9776::$$$message_0098_0013_0002$$$::"...I wonder if Saber ate breakfast."[lr]::
9777::$$$message_0098_0013_0003$$$::Last night, Saber was nodding while eating her dinner.[lr]::
9778::$$$message_0098_0013_0004$$$::Based on her behavior, it's not like she doesn't need food.::
9779::$$$message_0098_0014_0000$$$::"I didn't prepare lunch for her, so she must be hungry."[lr]::
9780::$$$message_0098_0014_0001$$$::Once Fuji-nee and Sakura go home, I should warm some dinner up for Saber.[lr]::
9781::$$$message_0098_0014_0002$$$::She'll have to eat alone, but there's nothing we can do about that.::
9782::$$$message_0098_0015_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
9783::$$$message_0098_0015_0001$$$::It's just...[lr]::
9784::$$$message_0098_0015_0002$$$::Imagining Saber eating by herself is making me mad.::
9785::$$$message_0098_0016_0000$$$::"Shirou, are you awake?"[lr]::
9786::$$$message_0098_0016_0001$$$::Tohsaka knocks on my door and peeks her head in.::
9787::$$$message_0098_0017_0000$$$::"Tohsaka? What's going on?"[lr]::
9788::$$$message_0098_0017_0001$$$::"Nothing. Dinner's ready, so come on out."[lr]::
9789::$$$message_0098_0017_0002$$$::   It's already that time?[lr]::
9790::$$$message_0098_0017_0003$$$::I pick myself up, glance toward Saber's room, and head into the hallway.::
9791::$$$message_0098_0018_0000$$$::"Oh there you are. Look at all the dishes! Can you believe it!? Tohsaka can cook Chinese cuisine...something that has long been absent from our menu!"[lr]::
9792::$$$message_0098_0018_0001$$$::Fuji-nee dances excitedly around the table, which is laid out with dinner.[lr]::
9793::$$$message_0098_0018_0002$$$::Now that she mentions it, it does all look to be Chinese dishes today.::
9794::$$$message_0098_0019_0000$$$::Four big plates decorate the table: crab meat with egg omelet, shredded beef with green peppers, a vegetable stir-fry with some fancy meat I've never seen before, and for some reason, a plate full of steamed shu-mai.::
9795::$$$message_0098_0020_0000$$$::Salad has been served on individual plates for everyone, and the setup seems to have been well thought out.[lr]::
9796::$$$message_0098_0020_0001$$$::It's pretty extravagant. Fuji-nee loves it.::
9797::$$$message_0098_0021_0000$$$::"This is a surprise. I thought you would make something Western."[lr]::
9798::$$$message_0098_0021_0001$$$::"Oh, she did consider making Western dishes, but when I mentioned that no one in this household makes Chinese dishes, she volunteered to make some."::
9799::$$$message_0098_0022_0000$$$::"Why would she set out to do something no one else does? Hm? Hey, Sakura, you and Tohsaka came home at the same time. Did you two go shopping together or something?"[lr]::
9800::$$$message_0098_0022_0001$$$::"Yes. Miss Tohsaka waited for me until the kyudou club's practice ended and we decided to shop for groceries on our way home."::
9801::$$$message_0098_0023_0000$$$::"I had no idea. Looks like you two are closer than I thought."[lr]::
9802::$$$message_0098_0023_0001$$$::"That may be true. Miss Tohsaka speaks to me often at school too. I don't know what made her take a liking to me, but she has been very kind to me ever since I came to this school."[lr]::
9803::$$$message_0098_0023_0002$$$::Huh.[lr]::
9804::$$$message_0098_0023_0003$$$::So Tohsaka really [font italic=true]is[font italic=false] a nice upperclassmen.::
9805::$$$message_0098_0024_0000$$$::"Enough yapping! Let's eat. I'm so hungry."[lr]::
9806::$$$message_0098_0024_0001$$$::Fuji-nee sits down excitedly.[lr]::
9807::$$$message_0098_0024_0002$$$::"You heard her. You two should sit down. Chinese food gets criminally bad when it's cold."[lr]::
9808::$$$message_0098_0024_0003$$$::Tohsaka sits down after she tells us to do the same.::
9809::$$$message_0098_0025_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
9810::$$$message_0098_0025_0001$$$::I sit down without a word.[lr]::
9811::$$$message_0098_0025_0002$$$::Everyone bows and thanks Tohsaka for cooking, then starts eating.::
9812::$$$message_0098_0026_0000$$$::"...Whoa!"[lr]::
9813::$$$message_0098_0026_0001$$$::I hate to admit it, but it's good.[lr]::
9814::$$$message_0098_0026_0002$$$::I've never cooked Chinese food because I've always thought it all tastes the same. But Tohsaka's dishes make me realize it had all just been bias on my part, and I find myself regretting that.::
9815::$$$message_0098_0027_0000$$$::"Wow, this is amazing! It's been a while since I've had a dish that goes so well with rice! Yep, I'm giving you full marks for this one!"[lr]::
9816::$$$message_0098_0027_0001$$$::"Thank you very much. I'm delighted to get such an honest opinion from someone like you."::
9817::$$$message_0098_0028_0000$$$::"Yes, I also see Chinese food in a new light. I don't usually like eating spicy dishes, but this is delicious!"[lr]::
9818::$$$message_0098_0028_0001$$$::Sakura looks pleased, seeming to enjoy the food too.::
9819::$$$message_0098_0029_0000$$$::After seeing everyone's happy faces, Tohsaka...[lr]::
9820::$$$message_0098_0029_0001$$$::"Heh."[lr]::
9821::$$$message_0098_0029_0002$$$::She turns to face me, her face triumphant.::
9822::$$$message_0098_0030_0000$$$::"What? You look like you have something to say."[lr]::
9823::$$$message_0098_0030_0001$$$::"Nothing! I'm just glad everyone liked it. Well, there's one person not being honest about his feelings, but it's amusing me so I'll let it slide. I understand how bad it must feel to be beaten at something you're good at."::
9824::$$$message_0098_0031_0000$$$::"Gngh! I get it. You made me cook dinner last night because you wanted to assess my cooking!"[lr]::
9825::$$$message_0098_0031_0001$$$::"Fufufufu. Okay. Today's lesson: never let anyone see your plans or potential!"[lr]::
9826::$$$message_0098_0031_0002$$$::Tohsaka returns to her food, looking exceedingly pleased with herself.::

